      "content": "That's a good start for the tone. To make it feel even more authentic to the period, can you make it a bit more descriptive about the people themselves? Like, how he perceives their appearance, their lack of \"proper\" technology or structure, and why he thinks they are fundamentally incapable of governing themselves without outside help? Just trying to capture that specific colonial mindset for the character's internal monologue.",
